-- Inserir integração demo do Strava para user ID 1
INSERT INTO user_integrations (user_id, provider, access_token, refresh_token, expires_at, athlete_id, scope, created_at, updated_at)
VALUES (1, 'strava', 'demo_access_token', 'demo_refresh_token', DATE_ADD(NOW(), INTERVAL 6 HOUR), 'demo_athlete_123', 'activity:read_all,read', NOW(), NOW())
ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE updated_at = NOW();

-- Inserir atividades demo realistas
INSERT INTO activities (user_id, provider, external_id, name, type, distance, duration, average_heartrate, max_heartrate, start_date, created_at, updated_at) VALUES
(1, 'strava', 'demo_1', 'Treino Intervalado Matinal', 'Run', 10500, 3240, 165, 182, DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 1 DAY), NOW(), NOW()),

(1, 'strava', 'demo_4', 'Corrida Recuperação', 'Run', 8000, 3000, 138, 152, DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 4 DAY), NOW(), NOW()),
(1, 'strava', 'demo_5', 'Brick: Bike + Run', 'Workout', 45000, 7200, 155, 175, DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 5 DAY), NOW(), NOW()),
(1, 'strava', 'demo_6', 'Treino de Força + Corrida', 'Run', 5000, 1800, 148, 165, DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 6 DAY), NOW(), NOW()),
(1, 'strava', 'demo_7', 'Ciclismo Intervalos', 'Ride', 60000, 7200, 158, 178, DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 7 DAY), NOW(), NOW())
ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE updated_at = NOW();
